deleteUint256(bytes32,uint256).details: Deletes an element from the array identified by the key. When an element is deleted from an Array, last element of that array is moved to the index of deleted element.

params._index: Index of the element to delete
params._key: Unique key to identify the array

insertUint256(bytes32,uint256).details: Inserts a uint256 element to the array identified by the key

params._data: Element to push into the array
params._key: Unique key to identify the array

insertUint256Multi(bytes32[],uint256[]).details: Inserts multiple uint256 elements to the array identified by the respective keys

params._data: Array of data to be inserted in arrays of the respective keys
params._keys: Array of keys to identify the data

setSecurityToken(address).details: Changes security token atatched to this data store

setUint256(bytes32,uint256).details: Stores a uint256 data against a key

params._data: Data to be stored against the key
params._key: Unique key to identify the data

setUint256Array(bytes32,uint256[]).details: Stores a uint256 array against a key

params._data: Array to be stored against the key
params._key: Unique key to identify the array

setUint256Multi(bytes32[],uint256[]).details: Stores multiple uint256 data against respective keys

params._data: Array of data to be stored against the respective keys
params._keys: Array of keys to identify the data
